Here's the relevant code snippet from `components/FloatingTabBar.tsx`:

```javascript
 React.useEffect(() => {
    if (activeTabIndex >= 0) {
      animatedValue.value = withSpring(activeTabIndex, {
        damping: 20,
        stiffness: 120,
        mass: 1,
      });
